                        "description": "Transfer money to another user.\n\n**Validation Rules:**\n- `receiver_id`: Required, must exist, cannot be yourself\n- `amount`: Required, numeric, min: 0.01, max: 1,000,000\n\n**Commission:**\n- 1.5% commission is automatically calculated and deducted from sender\n- Total debit = amount + commission\n\n**Rate Limiting:**\n- 60 requests per minute per user\n\n**Real-time Broadcasting (Pusher):**\n- After successful transfer, a `money.transferred` event is broadcast via Pusher\n- Event is sent to private channels for both sender and receiver: `user.{userId}`\n- Event data includes: transaction_id, amounts, commission, new balances, timestamp\n- Frontend can listen to this event to update UI in real-time without page refresh"
